snippet.title: Potatoman Seeks The Troof Trailer (iOS / Steam)
snippet.description:
iOS Store: https://itunes.apple.com/app/potatoman-seeks-the-troof/id954585437

Steam Store: http://store.steampowered.com/app/328500/

Potatoman will put your reflexes and worldview to the test as you guide him through dry deserts, mysterious forests, busy cities, the tallest mountains and eventually his innermost consciousness in search of the ultimate answer. Go forward, seek, and discover The Troof!
